                <note rend="inline" type="source">551.5F1/161: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Paraphrase]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Geneva</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-09-20T12:00:00+01:00"
                            >September 20, 1931—12 noon</date>.<lb/>[Received September 20—9:25
                        a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>144. Legation’s 135, September 17, 6 p.m. Yesterday when the Financial Committee
                    met it was suddenly found that the Committee was in a position to conclude its
                    work, and an adjournment took place after a meeting held late at night. The
                    Financial Committee members have left. Out of consideration for the
                    apprehensions set forth in the Department’s 108, September 16, 4 p.m., Davis
                    took no action to cause the adoption of the silver resolution.</p>
                <p>Davis sails for home at the end of this week and will discuss matter with you in
                    detail upon arrival.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wilson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
